## Safety Boundaries

- Do not store secrets, private keys, tokens, decrypted env files, kubeconfigs, or credentials in `.task-workspace/`.
- Do not edit source repo code from a task workspace.
- Task sessions should prepare and edit the /tmp code workspace recorded in `local.json`.
- Keep each running session scoped to one active task unless the user explicitly asks otherwise.
